tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Students (
    student_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_name VARCHAR,
    course_id INT,
    course_name VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE students (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
name STRING,
course_id INT,
grades FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE courses (course_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
course_name STRING,
instructor STRING,
description STRING);

CREATE TABLE datasets (dataset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
dataset_name STRING,
student_id INT,
completed BOOLEAN);

CREATE TABLE courses (
    course_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    course_name VARCHAR(50),
    instructor_id INT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
